&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src= &#34;https://pan.weidows.tech/d/local/img/loading.svg&#34; data-lazy-src=&#34;https://pan.weidows.tech/d/local/blog/Gh21vg.png&#34; alt=&#34;&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
